y%20appeared%20to%20slam%20the%20Federation%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20regard%20for%20norms%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20functions%20out%20of%20former%20officer%20bearers%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20come%20after%20the%20newly%20elected%20and%20controversial%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh%20announced%20that%20Under-15%20and%20Under-20%20nationals%20will%20take%20place%20at%20Nandini%20Nagar%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gonda%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20which%20the%20sports%20ministry%20called%20%E2%80%9Chasty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%2C%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2021)%2C%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20body.%20He%20is%20close%20to%20its%20former%20head%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20and%20strongman%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20whose%20ouster%20had%20been%20demanded%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20wrestlers.%20Brij%20Bhushan%20is%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20no%20fewer%20than%20seven%20wrestlers.%20During%20their%20protracted%20protest%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20also%20said%20Brij%20Bhushan%20and%20his%20coterie%20had%20complete%20and%20authoritarian%20control%20over%20the%20running%20of%20the%20sport%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGonda%20is%20understood%20to%20be%20Brij%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20sports%20ministry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fgovt-suspends-wrestling-federation-new-body-complete-control-former-office-bearers-9080900%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20notes%20that%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20shown%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98blatant%20disregard%20for%20the%20established%20legal%20and%20procedural%20norms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlympics%20bronze%20medalist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20had%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20election%2C%20announced%20that%20she%20is%20giving%20up%20the%20sport%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%20Olympian%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20Deaflympics%20gold%20medallist%20Virender%20Singh%20Yadav%20have%20returned%20their%20medals%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20awards%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20evening%2C%20Malik%20had%20posed%20on%20concerns%20voiced%20by%20junior%20wrestlers%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGonda%20is%20the%20area%20of%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BBrijbhushan.%20Now%20imagine%20in%20what%20environment%20the%20junior%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20go%20there%20to%20wrestle.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIs%20there%20no%20place%20in%20this%20country%20to%20hold%20nationals%20other%20than%20Nandini%20Nagar%3F%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20ministry%20said%20the%20Gonda%20announcement%20did%20not%20give%20enough%20notice%20to%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20announcement%20is%20hasty%2C%20without%20giving%20sufficient%20notice%20to%20wrestlers%20who%20are%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20said%20nationals%20and%20without%20following%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20WFI%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Sanjay%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20won%20in%20a%2040-7%20sweep%20against%20former%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medalist%20Anita%20Sheoran%20%E2%80%93%2012%20of%20the%2015%20posts%20in%20which%20elections%20were%20held%20were%20taken%20up%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%E2%80%99s%20residence%20is%20also%20the%20Federation%E2%80%99s%20office.%20Sanjay%20Singh%20visited%20it%20immediately%20after%20his%20re-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20of%20the%20Federation%20is%20being%20run%20from%20the%20premises%20controlled%20by%20former%20office%20bearers%E2%80%A6Which%20is%20also%20alleged%20premises%20wherein%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20the%20players%20have%20been%20alleged%20and%20present%20the%20court%20is%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20sports%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20rounds%20of%20censure%2C%20in%20August%2C%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20was%20banned%20by%20the%20wrestling%20governing%20body%2C%20United%20World%20Wrestling%2C%20for%20failing%20to%20conduct%20its%20elections%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703398874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-suspend-sanjay-singh-gonda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20came%20after%20newly%20elected%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20a%20Brij%20Bhushan%20loyalist%2C%20announced%20that%20Under-15%20and%20Under-20%20nationals%20will%20take%20place%20at%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Gonda%2C%20which%20is%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20turf.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wrestling%20Body%20Suspended%20Over%20'Hasty%20Decisions'%20Day%20After%20Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20Ministry%20of%20India%20has%20suspended%20newly-formed%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20body%20led%20by%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20Singh%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20was%20elected%20the%20new%20president%20of%20the%20wrestling%20body%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0Sanjay%20Singh%20won%2040%20out%20of%2047%20votes%20in%20a%20sweeping%20victory%20over%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20a%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20who%20was%20backed%20by%20top%20wrestlers%20who%20had%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20earlier%20over%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20has%20earlier%20served%20as%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20wrestling%20body.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20WFI's%C2%A0last%20executive%20council%20and%20its%20joint%20secretary%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20over%20'hasty'%20announcements%20of%20national%20competitions%20and%20the%20sports%20ministry%20said%20that%20the%20move%20was%20made%20without%20'following%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20WFI'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20decisions%20are%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20Executive%20Committee%2C%20before%20which%20agendas%20are%20required%20to%20be%20placed%20for%20consideration.%20As%20per%20Article%20XI%20of%20the%20WFI%20%C2%A0constitution%20under%20the%20Heading%20%E2%80%98Notices%20and%20Quorum%20for%20Meetings'%2C%20%C2%A0minimum%20notice%20period%20for%20EC%20meeting%20is%2015%20clear%20days%20and%20quorum%20is%20of%201%2F3rd%20of%20representatives.%20Even%20for%20Emergency%20EC%20meeting%2C%20minimum%20notice%20period%20is%207%20clear%20days%20with%20quorum%20requirement%20of%201%2F3rd%20of%20representatives.%26quot%3B%20Sports%20Ministry%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20release%2C%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20further%20alleged%20that%20the%20newly-formed%20body%20seems%20to%20be%20completely%20in%20control%20of%20previous%20office%20bearers%20against%20whom%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNewly%20elected%20body%20appears%20to%20be%20in%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office%20bearers%20in%20complete%20disregard%20to%20the%20Sports%20Code%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20business%20of%20the%20Federation%20is%20being%20run%20from%20the%20premises%20controlled%20by%20former%20office%20bearers.%20Which%20is%20also%20alleged%20premises%20wherein%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20the%20players%20have%20been%20alleged%20and%20present%20the%20court%20is%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703398620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6djondcg_brij-bhushan-sanjay-singh-pti-650_650x400_21_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fsports-ministry-suspends-newly-formed-wrestling-federation-of-india-body-4732615%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sports%20Ministry%20of%20India%20has%20suspended%20newly-formed%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20body%20led%20by%20Sanjay%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fsports-ministry-suspends-newly-formed-wrestling-federation-of-india-body-4732615%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sports%20Ministry%20suspends%20newly-elected%20WFI%20body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703398187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106245982%2Cimgsize-165250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fmore-sports%2Fothers%2Fsports-ministry-suspends-newly-elected-wrestling-federation-of-india-body%2Farticleshow%2F106245914.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20newly-elected%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20body%20was%20on%20Sunday%20suspended%20by%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20after%20uproar%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20close%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh%20as%20its%20new%20chief%2C%20after%20which%20Olympic%20medal-winning%20wrestler%20Sakshi%20Malik%20announced%20her%20retirement%20from%20the%20sport%20while%20another%20Olympic%20medallist%20Bajrang%20Punia%20returned%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20award%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20their%20continued%20protest.%20Sanjay%20Singh%20announced%20U-15%20%26amp%3B%20U-20%20nationals%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Nandini%20Nagar%2C%20Gonda%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar%20Praises%20Gautam%20Adani%20Over%20Financial%20Help%20For%20New%20Tech%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Saturday%20thanked%20and%20praised%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani%20for%20his%20financial%20help%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20technology%20centre%20in%20Pune's%20Baramati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20was%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20robotic%20lab%20in%20the%20engineering%20department%20of%20Vidya%20Pratishthan%20in%20Baramati.%20Finolex%20J%20Power%20Systems%20Limited%20chairman%20Deepak%20Chabaria%20was%20also%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineering%20sector%20is%20changing%20rapidly%20and%20it's%20necessary%20to%20create%20a%20group%20(section)%20that%20is%20ready%20to%20accept%20these%20changes%20to%20move%20ahead%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20told%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20building%20the%20first%20centre%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20in%20India%20and%20the%20construction%20is%20underway.%20This%20project%20is%20going%20to%20cost%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20We%20have%20jumped%20into%20this%20work%20after%20arranging%20the%20money.%20Fortunately%2C%20after%20I%20requested%20two%20of%20our%20colleagues%20to%20help%20with%20this%2C%20they%20immediately%20extended%20their%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20veteran%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20Siphotech%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20important%20company%20in%20the%20construction%20sector%20in%20the%20country%2C%20They%20have%20decided%20to%20help%20the%20project%20with%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20them%20very%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Mr%20Adani%20sent%20a%20Rs%2025%20crore%20cheque%20for%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGautam%20Adani's%20name%20will%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20he%20has%20sent%20a%20cheque%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20to%20the%20institution.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20these%20two%2C%20we%20are%20setting%20up%20both%20these%20projects%20at%20this%20place%20today%20and%20work%20has%20also%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20chief%20also%20informed%20that%20from%20January%2017-22%2C%20an%20agri-exhibition%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Baramati%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Krushi%20Vikas%20Pratisthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20high-tech%20products%20come%20into%20the%20market%20using%20machines%2C%20electrical%2C%20electronic%20and%20computer%20branches%20together%20while%20building%20a%20manpower%20that%20is%20industry-driven.%20If%20this%20growing%20demand%20is%20to%20be%20met%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20need%20for%20skilled%20engineers%20with%20new%20technology%20in%20both%20the%20country%20and%20abroad.%20Considering%20all%20these%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%2C%20Vidya%20Pratishthan%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20first%20smart%20factory%20of%20a%20rural%20area%20at%20about%20four%20thousand%20square%20feet%20in%20Baramati%20for%20which%20work%20has%20also%20been%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNowadays%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20production%20is%20going%20to%20China%2C%20how%20can%20this%20flow%20be%20brought%20to%20India%3F%20This%20is%20an%20opportunity.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20empower%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20youth%20power.%20It%20is%20always%20said%20that%20India%20is%20a%20country%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20it%20has%20perseverance%2C%20so%20we%20must%20be%20ready%20to%20give%20him%20the%20technical%20training%20which%20is%20accepted%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publish