gement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tanuj%20Virwani%20to%20not%20have%20a%20big%20fat%20wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703395527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106245289%2Cimgsize-50900.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftanuj-virwanis-wedding-to-be-a-close-knit-family-affair-rather-than-a-big-fat-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F106245296.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106245296.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Tanuj%20Virwani%20is%20set%20to%20tie%20the%20knot%20with%20his%20longtime%20partner%20Tanya%20Jacob%20in%20an%20intimate%20ceremony%20at%20his%20farmhouse.%20The%20couple%20intends%20to%20have%20a%20scaled-down%20'size%20zero%20wedding'%2C%20avoiding%20the%20exhaustion%20that%20often%20comes%20with%20elaborate%20celebrations.%20Tanuj's%20mother%2C%20Rati%20Agnihotri%2C%20is%20supportive%20of%20the%20close-knit%20ceremony.%20The%20decision%20to%20get%20married%20was%20a%20practical%20one%20to%20bridge%20the%20geographical%20gap%20between%20Tanuj%20and%20Tanya%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Singapore.%20Tanuj%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20privacy%20in%20relationships%20and%20maintaining%20a%20balance%20between%20personal%20and%20public%20spheres.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Gujarat%20Hub%20Turns%20%26quot%3BGhost%20Town%26quot%3B%20After%20Work%20Hours.%20Solution%3A%20Liquor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20a%20truly%20global%20business%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20in%20a%20noteworthy%20development%2C%20lifted%20liquor%20prohibition%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20International%20Finance%20Tec-City%20(GIFT%20City)%20area%20in%20Gandhinagar.%20Under%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20clubs%20in%20the%20GIFT%20City%20area%20will%20be%20given%20permits%20for%20'wine%20and%20dine'%20facilities.%20While%20liquor%20can%20be%20consumed%20in%20these%20facilities%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20sell%20liquor%20bottles.%20A%20liquor%20access%20permit%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20all%20employees%2C%20owners%20and%20officials%20working%20in%20GIFT%20City.%20This%20means%20those%20officially%20working%20in%20GIFT%20City%20area%20and%20their%20official%20guests%20will%20be%20able%20to%20go%20to%20such%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%20and%20clubs%20for%20wine%20and%20dine%20facilities%20as%20per%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20and%20the%20business%20fraternity%20are%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20welcome%20change%20to%20attract%20national%20and%20international%20companies%20and%20talent%20in%20the%20GIFT%20City%20while%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%20has%20termed%20it%20as%20a%20retrograde%20step%20towards%20'cultural%20erosion'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20big%20step%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20as%20it%20has%20been%20a%20dry%20state%20since%20it%20was%20carved%20from%20Mumbai%20State%20and%20created%20in%201960.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20been%20rigorous%20about%20laws%20pertaining%20to%20prohibition%20for%20the%20locals%2C%20who%20can%20get%20liquor%20permits%20only%20on%20health%20grounds%2C%20that%20too%20just%20for%20people%20above%2040%20years%20of%20age.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20liquor%20law%20was%20made%20stricter%20with%20punishment%20up%20to%2010%20years%20along%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20for%20manufacturing%2C%20purchasing%2C%20selling%20or%20transporting%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20government%20was%20cognizant%20of%20losing%20revenue%20both%20in%20tourism%20and%20business.%20So%2C%20in%202006%2C%20the%20state%20government%20through%20an%20enactment%20allowed%20outsiders%20to%20obtain%20liquor%20permits%20from%20authorised%20liquor%20stores%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20travel%20tickets.%20There%20are%20around%2060-65%20hotels%20and%20clubs%20that%20have%20been%20given%20temporary%20licences%20for%20liquor%20shops%20to%20serve%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20the%20state's%20economy%20through%20foreign%20investments%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20set%20up%20Special%20Economic%20Zones%20(SEZs)%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20GIFT%20City%20is%20one%20such%20SEZ%2C%20with%20an%20integrated%20development%20on%20886%20acres%20of%20land%20which%20includes%20ultra-modern%20office%20spaces%2C%20residential%20apartments%2C%20schools%2C%20proposed%20hospital%2C%20five-star%20hotels%20and%20business%20club.%20GIFT%20City%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20India's%20first%20greenfield%20smart%20city%20and%20International%20Financial%20Services%20Centre%20(IFSC)%20being%20developed%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Singapore%20and%20Dubai.%20The%20central%20government%20implemented%20a%20major%20financial%20sector%20reform%20by%20establishing%20and%20operationalizing%20India's%20maiden%20International%20Financial%20Services%20Centre%20(IFSC)%20in%20GIFT%20City.%20As%20of%20June%202023%2C%20there%20are%2023%20multinational%20banks%3B%2035%20fintech%20entities%3B%20two%20international%20stock%20exchanges%20with%20average%20daily%20trading%20volumes%20of%20%2430.6%20billion%3B%20as%20well%20as%20India's%20first%20international%20bullion%20exchange%20with%2075%20operating%20jewellers.%20There%20are%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20people%20working%20in%20GIFT%20City.%20However%2C%20despite%20these%20developments%2C%20GIFT%20City%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20deserted%20place%20after%20office%20hours%20with%20not%20much%20to%20offer%20in%20terms%20of%20entertainment.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Singapore%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20an%20interview%20had%20called%20the%20GIFT%20City%20as%20a%20'ghost%20town%20after%20working%20hours'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20this%20step%20will%20be%20welcomed%20by%20those%20who%20are%20visitors%20to%20the%20state%20on%20business%20trips.%20They%20can%20relax%20and%20have%20a%20good%20time%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20hard%20work.%20It's%20not%20about%20getting%20drunk%20but%20for%20some%20people%2C%20it's%20a%20cultural%20thing.%20It%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20attracting%20expatriates%20to%20Gujarat%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Marina%20Bhandari%2C%20an%20expat%20staying%20in%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20about%20the%20effort%2C%20Ms%20Bhandari%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20an%20expat%20like%20me%2C%20it%20will%20be%20absolutely%20wonderful%20to%20go%20out%20and%20have%20a%20drink%20instead%20of%20worrying%20about%20renewal%20of%20permit%20and%20stocking%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20itself%2C%20the%20GIFT%20management%20had%20written%20to%20the%20superintendent%20of%20prohibition%20and%20excise%20seeking%20a%20relaxation%20in%20liquor%20laws%20in%20the%20special%20economic%20zone%20(SEZ)%20area%20of%20the%20GIFT%20City.%20The%20request%20was%20to%20enable%20'evening%20public%20social%20life'%2C%20at%20par%20with%20what%20is%20enjoyed%20by%20professionals%20in%20other%20finance%20and%20technology%20hubs%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20said%20sources%20in%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BSince%202021%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20thinking%20on%20the%20proposal%20to%20relax%20prohibition%20rules%20in%20GIFT%20City.%20This%20has%20been%20initiated%20to%20entice%20national%20and%20international%20fintech%20firms%20to%20set%20up%20offices%20and%20to%20get%20top%20talent%20to%20shift%20base%20to%20the%20state%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20government%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20liquor%20is%20out%20of%20purview%20of%20GST%2C%20it%20will%20attract%20state%20VAT%20and%20excise%20duty%20which%20will%20earn%20revenue%20for%20the%20state.%20Also%2C%20liquor%20comes%20under%20the%20category%20of%20'sin%20goods'%2C%20it%20will%20be%20taxed%20heavily.%20Revenue%20will%20be%20generated%20by%20the%20GST%20department%20also%20due%20to%20thriving%20food%20business%20at%20the%20liquor%20serving%20restaurants%20and%20hotels%20in%20the%20GIFT%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20view%20that%20uplifting%20prohibition%20in%20GIFT%20City%20will%20have%20its%20negatives.%20Law%20and%20order%20and%20safety%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20country%20may%20be%20impacted.%20So%20may%20road%20accident%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaktisinh%20Gohil%2C%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Gujarat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGujarat's%20ethos%20will%20get%20impacted.%20It's%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20lift%20the%20ban%20on%20prohibition%20in%20GIFT%20City.%20God%20knows%20what's%20the%20compulsion.%20Who%20has%20paid%20and%20influenced%20them%20to%20lift%20it%20in%20the%20GIFT%20city%20when%20the%20prohibition%20prevails%20throughout%20the%20state%3F%20Instead%20of%20tightening%20the%20implementation%2C%20they%20have%20relaxed%20it%20to%20suit%20vested%20interests.%20This%20is%20a%20step%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20through%20the%20back%20door%20for%20the%20entry%20of%20liquor%20in%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prohibition%20exemption%20in%20the%20GIFT%20City%20is%20a%20positive%20experiment%20on%20part%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government.%20If%20one%20draws%20comparison%2C%20a%20successful%20model%20exists%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20where%20there%20are%20exclusive%20compounds%20for%20expats%20with%20all%20facilities%20like%20in%20western%20countries%20inside%20the%20premises.%20Life%20outside%20the%20compound%20is%20different%20and%20regulated%20strictly.%20While%20the%20GIFT%20City%20might%20offer%20the%20opportunity%20to%20drink%20inside%20the%20premises%2C%20upon%20meeting%20the%20set%20guidelines%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20authorities%20to%20stop%20pilferages%20of%20liquor%20as%20well%20as%20cases%20of%20drunken%20driving%20endangering%20lives%20of%20people.%20One%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20this%20well-thought%20decision%20adds%20revenue%20to%20the%20state%20coffers%20but%20doesn't%20negatively%20impact%20the%20strong%20social%20fabric%2C%20road%20safety%20or%20safety%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703395500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-10%2Fgift-city-gujarat_650x400_61476990227.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-gujarat-hub-turns-ghost-town-after-work-hours-solution-liquor-4732449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20a%20truly%20global%20business%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20in%20a%20noteworthy%20development%2C%20lifted%20liquor%20prohibition%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20International%20Finance%20Tec-City%20(GIFT%20City)%20area%20in%20Gandhinagar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-gujarat-hub-turns-ghost-town-after-work-hours-solution-liquor-4732449%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-gujarat-hub-turns-ghost-town-after-work-hours-solution-liquor-4732449%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-gujarat-hub-turns-ghost-town-after-work-hours-solution-liquor-4732449%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kashmir%3A%20Militants%20Shoot%20Dead%20Retired%20Top%20Cop%20Whose%20Security%20Detail%20Was%20Recently%20Withdrawn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24105313%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Suspected%20militants%20shot%20dead%20a%20top%20retired%20police%20officer%20inside%20a%20mosque%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Baramulla%20district%20on%20Sunday%2C%20December%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Mohammad%20Shafi%20Mir%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20a%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SSP)%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20in%202012.%20He%20had%20been%20a%20protected%20person%20with%20one%20security%20officer%20deployed%20with%20him%20round-the-clock%20who%20was%20withdrawn%20recently%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fretired-police-officer-shot-dead-by-militants-at-mosque-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-baramulla-9080793%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Gantmulla%20village%20of%20Sheeri%2C%20which%20falls%20between%20Baramulla%20and%20Uri%20towns%20in%20this%20north%20Kashmir%20frontier%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTerrorists%20fired%20upon%20Shri%20Mohd%20Shafi%2C%20a%20retired%20officer%20at%20Gantmulla%2C%20Sheeri%20%23Baramulla%20while%20praying%20Azan%20(morning%20call%20for%20prayer)%20in%20the%20mosque%20and%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%2C%E2%80%9D%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafi%2C%20who%20had%20devoted%20himself%20to%20social%20service%20after%20retirement%2C%20was%20a%20muezzin%20at%20a%20local%20mosque%20in%20his%20village%20where%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20issue%20a%20pre-dawn%20call%20for%20prayers%20on%20Sunday%20morning%20when%20the%20attack%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20news%20of%20the%20shootout%20spread%2C%20Shafi%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20plunged%20into%20shock%20and%20grief.%20Additional%20security%20personnel%20were%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%20and%20carried%20out%20searches%20to%20track%20down%20the%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20attack%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20spate%20of%20targeted%20killings%20in%20which%20members%20of%20the%20minority%20Pandit%20community%20and%20migrant%20workers%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20militants%20in%202021%20across%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retired%20SSP%E2%80%99s%20killing%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20police%20constable%20was%20shot%20and%20injured%20in%20a%20targeted%20attack%20at%20Hamdaniya%20Colony%20in%20Bemina%20area%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%20an%20off-duty%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20head%20constable%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20similar%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Masroor%20Ahmad%20Wani%2C%20a%20police%20inspector%2C%20was%20shot%20while%20he%20was%20playing%20cricket%20at%20a%20ground%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Eidgah%20locality%20of%20Srinagar.%20After%20battling%20for%20life%20for%20several%20days%2C%20the%20victim%20was%20later%20shifted%20to%20AIIMS%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20where%20he%20succumbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20militant%20attacks%20with%20the%20casualties%20suffered%20by%20security%20forces%20this%20year%20surpassing%20the%202022%20figure%2C%20official%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20and%20two%20others%20were%20injured%20when%20militants%20ambushed%20two%20Army%20vehicles%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20site%20of%20an%20anti-militancy%20operation%20in%20Poonch%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20reeling%20under%20tensions%20after%20the%20families%20of%20the%20three%20civilians%2C%20who%20were%20picked%20by%20the%20army%20for%20questioning%20in%20connection%20with%2