manpreet's%20meoment%20of%20aggression%2C%20Deepti%20said%3A%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BAll%20those%20things%20happen%20in%20cricket%20in%20heat%20of%20the%20moment.%20Our%20focus%20was%20only%20on%20taking%20wickets%20and%20bowling%20dot%20balls.%20I%20do%20no%20have%20much%20to%20say%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Deepti%20said%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepti%2C%20who%20top-scored%20with%2078%20in%20India's%20first-innings%20total%20of%20406%2C%20said%20it%20would%20be%20crucial%20to%20strike%20early%20on%20the%20final%20day.%20%26quot%3BThe%20aim%20will%20be%20to%20take%20their%20remaining%20five%20wickets%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20can%20in%20the%20first%20half%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20lesser%20the%20target%20the%20better%20it%20would%20be%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ball%20was%20keeping%20low%20on%20the%20third%20day%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20first%20day.%20It%20was%20not%20that%20challenging%2C%20let's%20see%2C%20the%20wicket%20should%20help%20the%20bowlers%20more%20tomorrow%20(Sunday)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepti%20said%20Australia's%20change%20in%20approach%20worked%20well%20on%20the%20day.%20%26quot%3BThey%20did%20not%20play%20their%20usually%20aggressive%20game%20which%20they%20had%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20and%20it%20helped%20them%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20all-rounder%20Perry%20hoped%20an%20overall%20lead%20in%20excess%20of%20200%20should%20hold%20her%20side%20in%20good%20stead%20given%20there%20is%20just%20a%20day's%20play%20left%20in%20this%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20long%20is%20left%20and%20how%20many%20runs%20we%20have%20put%20on%20the%20board.%20But%20it%20really%20matters%20how%20long%20we%20have%20got%20to%20then%20bowl%20at%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Perry%20replied%20when%20asked%20what%20would%20be%20her%20team's%20target%20on%20the%20final%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPosit