%20at%20a%20high%20cost.%20The%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20borrowed%20Rs%2044%2C000%20crore%20in%202023%20alone%2C%20including%20a%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20while%20the%20poll%20code%20was%20in%20force.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20new%20government%20in%20place%2C%20the%20state%20government's%20coffers%20are%20empty%20as%20it%20stares%20at%20a%20long%20list%20of%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20has%2C%20however%2C%20assured%20in%20the%20Assembly%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20crisis%26quot%3B%20and%20no%20welfare%20scheme%20will%20stop%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20funds.%20%26quot%3BSome%20have%20raised%20issues%2C%20saying%20schemes%20will%20stop.%20This%20is%20an%20unnecessary%20fear.%20No%20scheme%2C%20including%20Ladli%20Laxmi%20Yojana%2C%20will%20be%20discontinued%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20added%20that%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20was%20like%20Ramayana%20and%20Gita%20and%20assured%20that%20all%20schemes%20of%20the%20previous%20government%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20Congress%20is%20not%20convinced.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Abbas%20Hafeez%20said%20every%20citizen%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20in%20debt.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20baby%20born%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20now%20in%20a%20Rs%2040%2C000%20debt.%20The%20BJP%20is%20continuously%20pushing%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20towards%20bankruptcy.%20When%20will%20they%20understand%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hafeez%20said%20if%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20and%20formed%20a%20government%2C%20it%20would%20have%20tried%20to%20find%20new%20sources%20of%20generating%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagdish%20Devda%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20the%20Congress%20should%20%26quot%3Bintrospect%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20crushing%20defeat%20instead%20of%20targeting%20the%20government%20over%20its%20debt.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20borrow.%20If%20needed%2C%20we%20will%20borrow%20for%20development%20works%20like%20road%20construction%2C%20irrigation%20projects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Devda%20alleged%20that%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20took%20loans%20too%2C%20but%20did%20not%20use%20them%20for%20development.%20Instead%2C%20they%20swindled%20the%20funds%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703392020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffn6l5ib8_mohan-yadav_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mohan-yadav-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4-lakh-crore-in-debt-madhya-pradesh-borrows-again-to-meet-bjps-promises-4732286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20he%20took%20oath%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20has%20sought%20a%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20loan%20from%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20to%20meet%20the%20state's%20expenditures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mohan-yadav-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4-lakh-crore-in-debt-madhya-pradesh-borrows-again-to-meet-bjps-promises-4732286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mohan-yadav-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4-lakh-crore-in-debt-madhya-pradesh-borrows-again-to-meet-bjps-promises-4732286%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-mohan-yadav-shivraj-singh-chouhan-4-lakh-crore-in-debt-madhya-pradesh-borrows-again-to-meet-bjps-promises-4732286%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay-Tiger%20make%20an%20entry%20on%20top%20of%20police%20car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703391907000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106244226%2Cimgsize-50258.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbade-mi