20dose%20of%20vaccine%20is%20needed%20against%20the%20subvariant%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20about%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Dr%20Arora%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20prevention%20is%20required%20for%20all%20those%20who%20are%2060%20years%20of%20age%20or%20older%2C%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20comorbidities%20and%20those%20who%20are%20on%20drugs%20that%20suppress%20our%20immunity%2C%20like%20cancer%20patients.%20If%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20precaution%20so%20far%2C%20then%20they%20are%20advised%20to%20take%20precaution%3B%20otherwise%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20any%20additional%20doses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20Covid-19%20new%20variant%20Jn.1%2C%20Dr%20NK%20Arora%2C%20Chairman%2C%20INSACOG%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Within%20India...from%20October%20last%20week%20and%20then%20till%20now%20in%20last%208%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%2022%20cases...there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20it%20is%20spreading%20very%20rapidly...Jn.1%20is%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20all%20the%20isolates%20so%20far.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfPyLgoPJrQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfPyLgoPJrQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1738577892194595196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INSACOG%20chief%20asserted%20that%20various%20subvariants%20of%20Omicron%20have%20been%20reported%20but%20none%20of%20them%20have%20increased%20severity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20week%20you%20hear%20something%20new%20coming%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20and%20then%20it%20spreads%20all%20over%20India.%20We%20have%20identified%20a%20large%20number%20of%20subvariants%2C%20over%20400%20subvariants%2C%20or%20mutations%20of%20this%20virus%2C%20and%20fortunately%2C%20none%20of%20these%20Omicron%20variants%20have%20really%20been%20associated%20with%20more%20severe%20disease%20or%20hospitalisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20the%20major%20symptoms%20of%20JN.1%2C%20highlighting%20that%20they%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20other%20subvariants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSymptoms%20are%20very%20similar%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20one%20cannot%20differentiate%20JN.1%20from%20other%20subvariants%20of%20Omicron%20like%20fever%2C%20nasal%20discharge%20and%20cough.%20There%20can%20be%20occasional%20diarrhoea%20and%20severe%20body%20aches%2C%20and%20usually%20they%20recover%20in%20two%20to%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20outlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Arora%20further%20said%20that%20though%20the%20cases%20are%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20those%20being%20hospitalised%20are%20a%20lesser%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20India%2C%20from%20October%20last%20week%20till%20now%20in%20last%208%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%2022%20cases.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20it%20is%20spreading%20very%20rapidly.%20JN.1%20is%20less%20than%201%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20the%20isolates%20so%20far.%20Recently%2C%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20has%20certainly%20increased%2C%20and%20the%20testing%20has%20also%20picked%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20increase%20in%20hospitalisation.%20We%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%20in%20Kerala%2C%20but%20I%20must%20also%20say%20that%20in%20other%20states%20where%20testing%20has%20increased%20recently%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20cases.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20increase%20in%20hospitalisation%20or%20severe%20disease%20that%20requires%20ventilation%20or%20results%20in%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20panic%20but%20that%20it%20requires%20vigilance.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20assure%20everybody%20that%20we%20need%20to%20be%20vigilant%2C%20but%20not%20panicky%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20multi-fold%20spurt%20in%20fresh%20Covid%20cases%20was%20noted%20in%20India%20over%20the%20past%2024%20hours%2C%20with%20Kerala%20contributing%20the%20majority%20of%20those.%20A%20total%20of%20423%20cases%20were%20reported%20and%20of%20which%20266%20were%20from%20Kerala%20and%2070%20from%20neighbouring%20Karnataka%2C%20Union%20health%20ministry%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20deaths%20were%20reported%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20active%20cases%20of%20Covid-19%20in%20the%20country%20was%20recorded%20at%203%2C420.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20recently%20classified%20JN.1%20as%20a%20variant%20of%20interest%2C%20distinct%20from%20its%20parent%20lineage%20BA.2.86.%20However%2C%20the%20global%20health%20body%20emphasised%20that%20the%20overall%20risk%20posed%20by%20JN.1%20remains%20low%20based%20on%20current%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20its%20rapidly%20increasing%20spread%2C%20WHO%20is%20classifying%20the%20variant%20JN.1%20as%20a%20separate%20variant%20of%20interest%20(VOI)%20from%20the%20parent%20lineage%20BA.2.86.%20It%20was%20previously%20classified%20as%20VOI%20as%20part%20of%20BA.2.86%20sublineages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20available%20evidence%2C%20the%20additional%20global%20public%20health%20risk%20posed%20by%20JN.1%20is%20currently%20evaluated%20as%20low.%20Despite%20this%2C%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20winter%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%2C%20JN.1%20could%20increase%20the%20burden%20of%20respiratory%20infections%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20had%20earlier%20said%20it%20was%20continuously%20monitoring%20the%20evidence%20and%20would%20update%20the%20JN.1%20risk%20evaluation%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703390580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fs6ih5kqo_delhi-covid-generic-_625x300_23_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-extra-vaccine-dose-needed-for-jn-1-subvariant-says-covid-panel-chief-nk-arora-4729893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20surge%20in%20COVID-19%20cases%20in%20India%20and%20the%20detection%20of%20a%20subvariant%20JN.1%2C%20India%20SARS-CoV-2%20Genomics%20Consortium%20(INSACOG)%20chief%20Dr%20NK%20Arora%20said%20that%20no%20additional%20dose%20of%20vaccine%20is%20needed%20against%20the%20subvariant%20at%20present.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-extra-vaccine-dose-needed-for-jn-1-subvariant-says-covid-panel-chief-nk-arora-4729893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-extra-vaccine-dose-needed-for-jn-1-subvariant-says-covid-panel-chief-nk-arora-4729893%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-extra-vaccine-dose-needed-for-jn-1-subvariant-says-covid-panel-chief-nk-arora-4729893%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan%20appeals%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Islamabad%20High%20Court's%20order%20on%20Toshakhana%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703389751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106244209%2Cimgsize-19650.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-imran-khan-appeals-in-supreme-court-against-islamabad-high-courts-order-on-toshakhana-case%2Farticleshow%2F106