20manager.%20He%20handles%20the%20local%20needs%20of%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20South%20Africa%20head%20coach%20Shukri%20Conrad%20on%20Saturday%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20India%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20breach%20their%20'Final%20Frontier'%20in%20the%20upcoming%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabada%20was%20rested%20from%20the%20white%20ball%20leg%20as%20he%20was%20nursing%20a%20heel%20niggle%20while%20Ngidi%20pulled%20out%20after%20sustaining%20a%20left%20ankle%20injury%20ahead%20of%20the%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20afternoon%20though%2C%20Rabada%20and%20Nigidi%20bowled%20full%20tilt%20at%20the%20centre%20training%20wicket%20of%20the%20Supersport%20Park%20and%20facing%20them%20was%20Dean%20Elgar%2C%20who%20is%20playing%20in%20his%20last%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centurion%20track%20is%20a%20pacer's%20dream%20although%20India%20did%20get%20the%20better%20of%20South%20Africa%20last%20time%20around.%20The%20head%20coach%20would%20want%20his%20lethal%20weapons%20to%20fire%20on%20all%20cylinders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703386980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fnra5qubo_ashwin-r-venkatesh_625x300_23_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fr-ashwin-reveals-one-of-the-biggest-enemies-of-indian-cricket-team-know-more-about-the-man-4729963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20first%20India%20vs%20South%20Africa%20Test%20in%20Centurion%2C%20Ravichandran%20introduced%20a%20special%20person%20in%20a%20video%20vlog%20on%20Saturday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fr-ashwin-reveals-one-of-the-biggest-enemies-of-indian-cricket-team-know-more-about-the-man-4729963%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org