%20coating.%20Remember%20to%20turn%20off%20and%20unplug%20your%20phone%20before%20cleaning%2C%20and%20let%20the%20screen%20air%20dry%20completely%20before%20putting%20the%20case%20back%20on.%20Avoid%20using%20paper%20towels%20and%20tissues%2C%20as%20they%20can%20scratch%20the%20screen.%20Also%2C%20avoid%20spraying%20or%20pouring%20liquids%20directly%20onto%20the%20screen%2C%20as%20this%20can%20cause%20damage.%20Make%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20clean%20your%20phone%20screen%20regularly%20for%20a%20clean%20and%20hygienic%20device.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fcleaning-your-smartphone-screen-what-to-do-and-not-to-do%2Farticleshow%2F106242932.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Next%20For%20Indians%20Stuck%20In%20France%3F%20Court%20To%20Decide%20On%20Extending%20Stay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Indians%2C%20including%20unaccompanied%20minors%2C%20remain%20stuck%20at%20an%20airport%20in%20France%20after%20local%20authorities%20yesterday%20grounded%20their%20plane%20over%20suspected%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20trafficking%26quot%3B.%20The%20Nicaragua-bound%20charter%20plane%20from%20Dubai%20was%20carrying%20303%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Indians.%20It%20was%20grounded%20on%20Saturday%20during%20a%20technical%20halt%20at%20Vatry%20airport%20near%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20French%20judge%2C%20who%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20extend%20the%20detention%20of%20the%20passengers%20by%20eight%20days%2C%20is%20due%20to%20hear%20the%20case%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20border%20cops%20can%20hold%20a%20foreign%20national%20for%20up%20to%20four%20days%20if%20they%20land%20in%20the%20country%20and%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20travel%20further.%20This%20can%20be%20extended%20for%20eight%20days%20a%20few%20times%20-%20and%20up%20to%2026%20days%20in%20total%20-%20in%20exceptional%20case