t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportskeeda%3C%2Fa%3E's%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20asked%2C%20what%20if%20the%20BCCI%20had%20never%20started%20the%20IPL.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20would%20have%20been%20the%20worst%20decision%20made%20by%20BCCI%20because%20IPL%20is%20the%20best%20thing%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20Indian%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20several%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20window%20to%20organise%20IPL%202024%20is%20from%20March%2022%20to%20May%20end.%20The%20final%20dates%20for%20the%2017th%20season%20of%20IPL%20will%20be%20announced%20once%20the%20dates%20for%20India's%20general%20elections%20are%20finalised%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Australia's%20World%20Cup-winning%20pacer%2C%20became%20the%20most%20expensive%20player%20in%20the%20history%20of%20IPL%2C%20after%20he%20was%20bought%20for%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20by%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20in%20the%20auction%20on%20December%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-arm%20pacer%20became%20the%20second%20player%20to%20breach%20the%2020-crore%20mark%20after%20team-mate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20bought%20by%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20for%20Rs%2020.5%20crore%20on%20the%20same%20day%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20auction%20held%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2072%20players%20(30%20overseas)%20were%20picked%20as%20the%20teams%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20230.45%20crore%20in%20the%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harshal%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1293-harshal-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHars