alt%3D%5C%22Catherine%20Boudreau%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20senior%20sustainability%20reporter%2C%20swims%20at%20Dubai's%20AquaVenture%20water%20park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6580d16150edbc52a8658294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222583%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESunset%20on%20the%20Palm%20Jumeirah%2C%20where%20the%20Aquaventure%20water%20park%20is%20located.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20favorite%20tourist%20attraction%20in%20Dubai%20was%20the%20water%20park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20day%20cost%20about%20%24175%2C%20including%20a%20day%20pass%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20a%20waterproof%20pouch%20for%20my%20iPhone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%A0The%20park%20has%20rides%20for%20adrenaline%20junkies%20and%20families%2C%20from%20lazy%20rivers%20to%20steep%20slides.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20two%20weeks%20in%20Dubai%20reporting%20on%20the%20UN%20climate%20conference%20for%20Business%20Insider%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20time%20for%20some%20sightseeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20choose%20because%20the%20city%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20famous%20attractions%2C%20including%20the%20world's%20largest%20mall%2C%20flower%20garden%2C%20and%20picture%20frame%2C%20plus%20the%20Burj%20Khalifa%2C%20the%20world's%20tallest%20skyscraper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20an%20adrenaline%20rush%20and%20the%20beach%2C%20so%20I%20visited%20the%20world's%20largest%20water%20park%2C%20Aquaventure%2C%20with%20other%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20on%20a%20weekday%2C%20so%20the%20lines%20weren't%20long.%20The%20park%20has%20a%20nearly%2060-foot%20plunge%20for%20thrill%20seekers%20like%20me%2C%20plus%20lazy%20rivers%20and%20a%20beautiful%20beach%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20relax.%20There%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.kerzner.com%2Fapi%2Fpublic%2Fcontent%2F6f561571344d4e46b89bd99416bce2e6%3Fv%3D45a5094c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20three%20towers%20and%20at%20least%2050%20water%20slides%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20visit%20them%20all%2C%20prepare%20to%20walk%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWear%20whatever%20bathing%20suit%20you%20own%20%E2%80%94%20modesty%20rules%20don't%20apply%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it%20was%20like%2C%20plus%20a%20few%20tips%20if%20you%20decide%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20park%20is%20on%20the%20tip%20of%20Palm%20Jumeirah%2C%20a%20manmade%20island%20shaped%20like%20a%20palm%20tree.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Google%20Maps%20showing%20the%20location%20of%20Aquaventure.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658364bbcefc010bea25eb06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAquaventure%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20Palm%20Jumeirah.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Maps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAquaventure%20is%20part%20of%20the%20resort%20Atlantis%2C%20The%20Palm%2C%20which%20opened%20in%20September%202008.%20It's%20since%20become%20the%20biggest%20waterpark%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalnews.com%2Ftravel%2Fnews%2F2022%2F10%2F05%2Fdubais-atlantis-aquaventure-sets-new-guinness-world-record-with-50-water-slides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%20at%2022%20hectares%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%2054%20acres%2C%20following%20an%20expansion%20completed%20in%202021.%20A%20new%20water%20slide%20tower%20and%20splash%20pools%20were%20added%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20attractions%20to%20105.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBuy%20a%20ticket%20online.%20It%20costs%20%2485%2C%20versus%20about%20%2497%20at%20the%20park.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20Atlantis%2C%20The%20Palm%20resort%20from%20the%20monorail.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65843ca0cefc010bea26178b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20Atlantis%2C%20The%20Palm%20resort%20from%20the%20monorail.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20buying%20a%20day%20pass%20at%20Aquaventure.%20Save%20yourself%20%2412%20and%20use%20it%20toward%20other%20purchases.%20A%20daily%20locker%20rental%20is%20about%20%247.%20I%20bought%20a%20%2420%20waterproof%20pouch%20for%20my%20iPhone%20to%20take%20photos.%20It%20was%20worth%20it.%20My%20phone%20survived%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20slides%20and%20a%20swim%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recommend%20taking%20a%20cab%20if%20you're%20short%20on%20time%20to%20get%20to%20the%20water%20park%20and%20not%20staying%20in%20Palm%20Jumeirah.%20Local%20cabs%20(not%20Uber)%20are%20pretty%20affordable%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20you're%20staying.%20I%20rarely%20paid%20more%20than%20%2415%2C%20including%20tip%2C%20unless%20I%20was%20going%20toward%20busy%20downtown%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20on%20public%20transportation%20from%20my%20hotel%20in%20Dubai%20Marina%2C%20which%20took%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palmmonorail.com%2Fstations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonorail%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20travels%20across%20Palm%20Jumeirah%20is%20%248%20roundtrip%20but%20isn't%20connected%20to%20the%20city's%20larger%20metro%20system%2C%20so%20the%20transfer%20involves%20a%20long%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palmmonorail.com%2Fstations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20off%20the%20monorail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20must%20walk%20through%20a%20mall%20to%20get%20to%20Aquaventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20slides%20for%20thrill%20seekers%3A%20Leap%20of%20Faith%2C%20Poseidon's%20Revenge%2C%20Blackout%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20plunges%20down%20a%20water%20slide%20in%20a%20temple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65811d93a79e5746976accf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223436%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20film%20crew%20tapes%20a%20plunge%20down%20The%20Leap%20of%20Faith.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20our%20day%20with%20the%20Leap%20of%20Faith%2C%20a%2060-foot%20body%20slide.%20The%20clear%20tunnel%20apparently%20propels%20riders%20through%20a%20lagoon%20filled%20with%20sharks%2C%20but%20I%20closed%20my%20eyes%20%E2%80%94%20both%20out%20of%20fear%20and%20to%20avoid%20water%20in%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoseidon's%20Revenge%20was%20the%20most%20extreme%20%E2%80%94%20and%20exhilarating%20%E2%80%94vertical%20drop%20at%20Aquaventure.%20You%20stand%20in%20an%20enclosed%20tube%2C%20a%20countdown%20begins%2C%20and%20then%20the%20floor%20pulls%20out%20from%20under%20you.%20It's%20free%20fall%20into%20windy%20loops%20at%20nearly%2040%20miles%20an%20hour%2C%20or%2060%20kilometers%20per%20hour.%20Prepare%20for%20a%20slightly%20sore%20back%20from%20the%20water%20jets%20that%20help%20carry%20you%20down%20the%20slide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20tower%20to%20Blackout%20has%20stunning%20views%20of%20Palm%20Jumeirah.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Winding%20blue%20and%20purple%20water%20slides%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65812376a79e5746976acd5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlackout%20is%20the%20purple%20slide.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAquaventure%20says%20Blackout%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20tallest%20vertical%20drop%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B%20at%2048-meters%20tall%2C%20or%20about%20157%20feet.%20It's%20located%20at%20Trident%20Tower%2C%20the%20newest%20addition%20to%20Aquaventure%20that%20opened%20in%202021%20as%20part%20of%20the%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20group%20slides%3A%20Odyssey%20of%20Terror%20and%20Zoomerango%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20winding%20orange%20and%20blue%20water%20slides.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581124e1c5c7b8c9a098bc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20Odyssey%20of%20Terror%20(left)%20from%20the%20beach.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20Aquaventure%20is%20that%20riders%20don't%20have%20to%20lug%20heavy%20tubes%20up%20the%20stairs%20to%20most%20group%20slides.%20The%20tubes%20are%20sent%20up%20on%20conveyor%20belts%20on%20the%20side%20of%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20five%20people%20into%20a%20tube%20for%20the%20Odyssey%20of%20Terror.%20We%20cruised%20down%20a%20steep%20drop%20before%20speeding%20up%20a%20tall%20wall%20and%20plummeting%20down%20again.%20Our%20hearts%20were%20racing%20and%20we%20couldn't%20stop%20laughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EZoomerango%20also%20has%20steep%20drops%20and%20vertical%20walls.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20rides%20a%20round%20tube%20down%20a%20water%20slide%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65812c4c1c5c7b8c9a098d17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUp%20to%20six%20people%20can%20take%20the%20Zoomerango%20together.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20Zoomerango%20because%20you%20fly%20up%20a%20tall%20wall%20before%20cruising%20down%20into%20a%20splash%20pool.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20slides%20at%20Aquaventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPace%20yourself.%20The%20entire%20water%20park%20can't%20be%20done%20in%20a%20day.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tubers%20float%20in%20a%20lazy%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581a89aa79e5746976adc9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETubers%20float%20in%20one%20of%20the%20many%20lazy%20rivers%20at%20Aquaventure.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20visit%2C%20we%20prioritized%20taking%20all%20the%20high-adrenaline%20slides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20much%20more%20to%20see%20for%20those%20who%20want%20a%20calmer%20day.%20An%20area%20called%20Splashers%20Lagoon%20is%20only%20for%20families%20with%20kids.%20There's%20also%20a%20dolphin%20show%2C%20a%20large%20aquarium%2C%20lazy%20rivers%2C%20and%20a%20beautiful%20beach%20with%20calm%2C%20warm%20waters%20for%20swimming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fun%20to%20spend%20the%20day%20outdoors%20and%20beat%20the%20heat%20if%20you're%20in%20Dubai%20during%20hotter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-largest-water-park-dubai-aquaventure-thrill-seekers-dream-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703347381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581ab861c5c7b8c9a099e03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-largest-water-park-dubai-aquaventure-thrill-seekers-dream-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AquaVenture%20is%20the%20largest%20water%20park%20in%20the%20world%2C%20built%20for%20the%20adrenaline%20junkie.%20Its%20%24175%20for%20a%20day%20pass.%20Here's%20what%20is%20was%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-largest-water-park-d