id%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20so%20you%20know%2C%20that%20was%20a%20really%20bad%20decision%2C%20you%20know%2C%20right%3F%20That%20was%20a%20bad%20decision.%26quot%3B%20I%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BWas%20it%20a%20bad%20decision%20or%20did%20it%20have%20a%20bad%20outcome%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that's%20the%20key%20to%20poker%3A%20To%20flip%20that%20question%20back%20on%20others%20that%20might%20give%20you%20some%20adversity%20because%20if%20you%20can%20separate%20bad%20decisions%20from%20bad%20outcomes%2C%20you'll%20be%20a%20great%20poker%20player.%20That%20realization%20was%20something%20that%20transformed%20my%20poker%20career.%20Just%20knowing%20that%20I%20belong%20and%20that%20a%20random%20guy%20at%20a%20table%20playing%20a%20%2420%20tournament%20isn't%20going%20to%20dictate%20how%20I%20feel%20about%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20studying.%20I%20kicked%20it%20into%20gear%20and%20started%20consuming%20as%20much%20poker%20content%20as%20I%20could.%20I%20became%20good%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20Poker%20Power%20teacher%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20confident%20in%20what%20I%20was%20saying%20because%20I%20had%20some%20results%20to%20back%20it%20up.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20start%20teaching%20other%20women%20to%20be%20in%20situations%20where%20they%20can%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20hell%20with%20all%20the%20other%20guys%20here.%20I'm%20going%20to%20take%20my%20seat.%20And%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20well.%20And%20you%20guys%20can't%20do%20anything%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mindset%20and%20the%20game%20itself%20are%20helpful%20in%20any%20workplace%20environment%2C%20especially%20in%20finance.%20In%20a%20financial%20environment%2C%20you%20will%20be%20the%20minority%20as%20a%20woman.%20So%20I%20think%20having%20the%20confidence%20to%20make%20your%20voice%20heard%20challenges%20the%20status%20quo.%20Women%20existing%20in%20or%20striving%20for%20positions%20of%20power%20is%20sometimes%20an%20uncomfortable%20feeling%20for%20men%2C%20and%20the%20only