%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20miners%20said%20that%20they%20had%20unwillingly%20accepted%20the%20cheques%20and%20would%20not%20encash%20them%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20miners%20initially%20declined%20the%20cheques%20from%20Dhami%2C%20the%20report%20quoted%20Wakeel%20Hassan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Delhi-based%20Rockwell%20Enterprises%20%E2%80%93%20which%20handled%20the%20final%20tunnel%20rescue%20%E2%80%93%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHassan%20said%20that%20they%20were%20meted%20out%20%E2%80%9Cstep-motherly%20treatment%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20rescued%20from%20inside%20were%20given%20Rs%201%20lakh%20cheques%20immediately%20by%20the%20CM%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20who%20put%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20line%2C%20they%20are%20giving%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20We%20also%20said%20we%20do%20not%20want%20this%20Rs%2050%2C000%20reward%2C%20but%20if%20they%20want%20to%20do%20something%20for%20us%2C%20then%20set%20a%20milestone%20that%20if%20someone%20does%20something%20for%20India%2C%20the%20country%20does%20the%20same%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Hassan%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20asked%20them%20to%20either%20provide%20us%20with%20permanent%20jobs%20or%20give%20us%20an%20amount%20that%20can%20help%20us%20get%20out%20of%20this%20profession%20so%20that%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20keep%20digging%20holes%20our%20entire%20lives.%20We%20have%20made%20(the%20government)%20and%20India%20proud.%20This%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20a%20milestone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20Uttarakhand%20government%20of%20demeaning%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20rat-hole%20miners%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20