s%20with%20support%20from%20their%20male%20colleagues%3F%20Does%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20as%20it%20played%20out%20over%202023%20hold%20out%20hope%20for%20those%20who%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20premier%20sports%20bodies%20in%20India%20become%20more%20democratic%20and%20representative%20of%20the%20changing%20aspirations%20of%20a%20young%20India%20where%20the%20best%20talent%20has%20sprung%20from%20some%20of%20the%20most%20underprivileged%20social%20groups%3F%20In%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20this%20reality%2C%20the%20sports%20bodies%20remain%20mired%20either%20in%20the%20antics%20of%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20own%20version%20of%20%3Cem%3Eparivaarvaad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20sports%20minister%20held%20in%20June%202023%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20had%20put%20forward%20five%20demands.%20These%20were%20that%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20be%20arrested%20given%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20woman%20chief%20of%20the%20WFI%2C%20and%20that%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20or%20his%20family%20members%20should%20not%20be%20part%20of%20the%20WFI.%20They%20had%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20police%20case%20filed%20against%20them%20in%20May%2C%20the%20day%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20inaugurated%2C%20be%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03135106%2FFxNeRGbakAYEoSI-1024x686.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-656362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20stop%20protesting%20wrestlers%20from%20marching%20to%20new%20parliament%20building%20on%20May%2028.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40SakshiMalik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20delayed%20registration%20of%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%20in%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20and%20only%20after%20the%20matter%20went%20to%20court%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20gave%20ample%20time%20to%20the%20accused%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20complainants%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20alacrity%20shown%20in%20registering%20cases%20against%20the%20protestors.%20As%20on%20an%20earlier%20occasion%2C%20assurances%20were%20given%20to%20the%20protestors%20by%20the%20concerned%20(sic!)%20minister%20clearly%2C%20none%20of%20these%20have%20been%20fulfilled.%20Nor%20has%20any%20action%20been%20reportedly%20taken%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20failure%20to%20uphold%20the%20promise%20made%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20that%20Singh%20and%20his%20associates%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20by%20the%20sports%20minister%2Fministry%20gives%20the%20signal%20of%20impunity%20to%20those%20violating%20the%20law.%20The%20result%20was%20there%20for%20all%20to%20see%20when%20Sakshi%20Malik%20hung%20up%20her%20boots%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20was%20ever%20any%20doubt%20that%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20a%20crime%20steeped%20and%20soaked%20in%20power%2C%20perhaps%20the%20WFI%20saga%20will%20dispel%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestlers-protest-to-wfi-elections-recap-of-what-happened-in-12-months-101703168955051-amp.html%5C%22%3Etimeline%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20heroic%20and%20unprecedented%20struggle%20by%20the%20wrestlers%20against%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20is%20forgotten%2C%20the%20visuals%20will%20continue%20to%20tell%20the%20story%3A%20of%20the%20courage%20shown%20by%20those%20who%20chose%20to%20speak%20up%3B%20of%20the%20families%2C%20farmers%20and%20women%20activists%20who%20came%20out%20in%20support%20to%20express%20their%20anger%20in%20public%3B%20of%20the%20police%20alternatively%20choosing%20to%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20shunning%20its%20duty%20and%20taking%20measures%20to%20arrest%20the%20protestors%20post%20haste%2C%20at%20the%20beck%20and%20call%20of%20their%20superiors.%20This%20record%20shall%20include%20the%20inglorious%20record%20of%20the%20official%20apathy%20and%20indifference%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20while%20showing%20overeagerness%20to%20shield%20those%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20migrants%20during%20Corona%20captured%20in%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20period%2C%20the%20footage%20of%20Olympians%20and%20international%20sports%20champions%20being%20dragged%20on%20the%20streets%20outside%20even%20as%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20being%20inaugurated%20on%20May%2028%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20numerous%20successes%20of%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%20These%20pictures%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%20strutting%20about%20with%20full%20freedom%20in%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20Parliament%20building%20even%20as%20the%20cries%20for%20justice%20of%20those%20who%20had%20brought%20fame%20and%20glory%20to%20the%20country%20could%20be%20heard%20outside%20%E2%80%93%20will%20challenge%20viewers%20to%20read%20the%20sub-text%20of%20the%20achievements%20on%20the%20governance%20front%20in%20India%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Vishwaguru%20in%20the%20times%20to%20come.%20Perhaps%20they%20will%20tell%20us%20more%20than%20the%20media%20analysts%20will%2C%20in%20times%20when%20those%20spinning%20the%20most%20successful%20yarns%20are%20bestowed%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20appointing%20fact-check%20bodies%20on%20whether%20online%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbrij-bhushan-singhs-loyalist-elected-as-the-chief-of-wrestling-federation-of-india%5C%22%3ESakshi%20Malik%20Quits%20Wrestling%20as%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Loyalist%20Elected%20as%20WFI%20Chief%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20lessons%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20these%20unfolding%20events.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20women%20in%20India%20have%20a%20long%20wait%20ahead%20for%20rampant%20sexual%20harassment%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20crime%20to%20be%20tackled%20head-on.%20The%20chances%20for%20women%20to%20get%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20and%20enjoy%20equality%20look%20more%20dim%20as%20this%20year%20ends%2C%20than%20they%20did%20in%20January%202023%2C%20when%20the%20star%20sportspersons%20first%20spoke%20up.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20crime%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20brazen%20might%20of%20power%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20bring%20it%20out%20in%20the%20open%20shall%20perhaps%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20a%20Verma%20Committee%2C%20which%20had%20argued%20that%20Army%20men%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20cover%20under%20AFSPA.%20The%20Justice%20Verma%20Committee%20had%20opined%20that%20%E2%80%9CPersonnel%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20offences%20in%20conflict%20areas%20should%20be%20tried%20under%20ordinary%20criminal%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20the%20spirit%20displayed%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20those%20accused%20in%20the%20WFI%20case%20may%20get%20away%20speaks%20of%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20then-unknown%20young%20woman%2C%20given%20the%20name%20of%20Nirbhaya%20by%20the%20media%2C%20shocked%20the%20nation%20and%20led%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Amendments%20enacted%20in%202013%2C%20followed%20by%20POSH.%20In%20contrast%20with%20the%20response%20in%202013%2C%20the%20cries%20of%20internationally%20acclaimed%20sportspersons%20for%20justice%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20silenced%20with%20the%20force%20of%20might.%20Amidst%20much%20else%20that%20they%20do%2C%20those%20in%20government%2C%20entrusted%20as%20per%20law%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20guilty%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20are%20punished%2C%20continue%20to%20preach%20to%20ordinary%20mortals%20about%20their%20duty%20towards%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20solidarity%20with%20the%20struggling%20wrestlers%2C%20who%20for%20now%20stand%20defeated%20and%20demoralised%2C%20women%20in%20India%20should%20set%20aside%20a%20special%20day%2F%20date%20to%20mark%20the%20need%20for%20continued%20struggle%20on%20this%20issue.%20Punishment%20of%20those%20guilty%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20if%20women%20are%20to%20advance%20their%20struggle%20for%20equality%2C%20including%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20work%20and%20employment.%20It%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20realised%20that%20measures%20such%20as%20reservations%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20in%20the%20legislatures%20will%20have%20meaning%20only%20if%20laws%20enacted%20to%20give%20strength%20to%20women%20are%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20contours%20of%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20do%20not%20encompass%20upholding%20the%20dignity%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sportswomen.%20That%20requires%20both%20political%20will%20on%20the%20part%20of%20governments%20in%20power%20as%20also%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people%20to%20hold%20governments%20and%20officials%20accountable.%20The%20saga%20of%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20struggle%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20%E2%80%93%20spread%20over%20the%20year%202023%20%E2%80%93%20underlines%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20struggle%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20women%20and%20punishment%20for%20those%20accused%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20is%20integrally%20linked%20to%20the%20struggle%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%20in%20times%20when%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20and%20their%20representatives%20choose%20to%20stand%20with%20those%20seen%20to%20be%20violating%20the%20law.%20The%20years%20to%20come%20may%20tell%20us%20more%20about%20how%20women%20in%20India%20look%20beyond%20the%20rhetorical%20invocation%20of%20tradition%20and%20false%20narratives%20of%20history%20to%20make%20constitutional%20guarantees%20a%20part%20of%20their%20everyday%20struggle%20for%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndu%20Agnihotri%20is%20an%20independent%20researcher%2C%20formerly%20Professor%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Development%20Studies%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703328844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155114%2FEffect-38.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwfi-saga-proves-once-again-that-sexual-harassment-is-a-crime-steeped-in-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20hope%20that%20the%20protests%20led%20by%20country's%20top%20women%20wrestlers%20would%20yield%20results%20in%20the%20form%20of%20punishment%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20was%20buried%20when%20former%20WFI%20president's%20close%20aide%20was%20elected%20as%20its%20new%20chief%20on%20December%2021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwfi-saga-proves-once-again-that-sexual-harassment-is-a-crime-steeped-in-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20Says%20Hijab%20Ban%20in%20State%20Schools%20Will%20Be%20Revoked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F09161033%2FUntitled-design-91.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20Friday%20(December%2022)%20that%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiddaramaiah%2Fstatus%2F1738206440685531179%5C%22%3Eordered%20the%20revocation%20of%20the%20ban%20on%20hijabs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%20at%20a%20function%20in%20Mysuru%20district%2C%20he%20said%20his%20government%20would%20revoke%20the%20ban%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20can%20wear%20the%20dress%20of%20their%20choice%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-chief-minister-says-he-has-asked-for-withdrawal-of-order-banning-hijab-in-classrooms%2Farticle67666503.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20instructed%20%5Bthe%20officials%5D%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20restriction%20from%20tomorrow%20%5BDecember%2023%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20portal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fno-more-hijab-ban-says-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-adds-clothes-food-are-individual-choices%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%20him%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20last%20year%2C%20the%20state%20government%2C%20then%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fjournal%2Fkarnataka-government-order-on-dress-code-for-students%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20students%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20in%20colleges%20falling%20under%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20pre-university%20education%20board%20must%20wear%20uniforms%20fixed%20by%20the%20state%20or%20the%20colleges%E2%80%99%20administrative%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20prohibited%20the%20use%20of%20clothes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthreaten%20equality%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20female%20students%20at%20a%20pre-university%20college%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Udupi%20district%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fkarnataka-muslim-students-college-udupi-hijab%5C%22%3Ebeing%20disallowed%20from%20entering%20their%20classroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20wearing%20the%20hijab%2C%20a%20headscarf%20traditionally%20worn%20by%20Muslim%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20ruled%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkarnataka-hijab-case-verdict%5C%22%3Ewearing%20the%20hijab%20was%20not%20an%20%E2%80%9Cessential%20religious%20practice%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Islam%20and%20that%20uniforms%20were%20a%20reasonable%20restriction%20on%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-hijab-ban-split-verdict%5C%22%3Edelivered%20a%20split%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20matter%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20added%20at%20the%20function%20on%20Friday%20that%20%E2%80%9Cyour%20choices%20are%20yours%20and%20my%20choices%20are%20mine.%20It%E2%80%99s%20that%20simple%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20wear%20dhoti%20and%20kurta%2C%20and%20you%20wear%20pant%20and%20shirt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20your%20choice.%20What%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20in%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkarnataka-to-withdraw-hijab-ban-order-announces-cm-siddaramaiah-9079434%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20post%20on%20X%20also%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20the%20work%20of%20dividing%20people%20and%20dividing%20society%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20clothes%2C%20dress%20%5Band%5D%20caste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20Siddaramaiah%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20revoking%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20government%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20allowing%20religious%20attire%20in%20educational%20institutions%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20is%20dividing%20young%20minds%20along%20religious%20lines%2C%20potentially%20hindering%20the%20inclusive%20learning%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karnataka%20BJP%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Flifting-hijab-ban-in-karnataka-raises-concern-about-secular-nature-of-educational-spaces-bjp%2Farticle67668627.ece%5C%22%3EB.Y.%20Vijayendra%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdupi%20MLA%20Yashpal%20Suvarna%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20challenge%20and%20protest%20Siddaramaiah%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703327489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F09161033%2FUntitled-design-91.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-says-hijab-ban-in-state-schools-will-be-revoked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20Siddaramaiah's%20decision%20to%20revoke%20the%20ban%2C%20saying%20that%20allowing%20religious%20attire%20in%20educational%20institutes%20would%20%E2%80%98divide%20young%20minds%20along%20religious%20lines%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-cm-siddaramaiah-says-hijab-ban-in-state-schools-will-be-revoked%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Civilians%20Killed%20in%20the%20Aftermath%20of%20Poonch%20Terror%20Attack%20Were%20Tortured%20to%20Death%2C%20Allege%20Families%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20families%20of%20three%20tribal%20men%20from%20Poonch%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20tortured%20to%20death%20by%20the%20Army%20after%20the%20attack%20in%20which%20five%20soldiers%20lost%20their%20lives%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20custodial%20killing%20of%20the%20three%20civilians%20identified%20as%20Safeer%20Hussain%2C%2037%2C%20Mohammed%20Showkat%2C%2026%20and%20Shabir%20Ahmed%2C%2032%2C%20all%20residents%20of%20Topa%20Mastandara%20village%20in%20Poonch%20district%2C%20had%20triggered%20protests%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Sarpanch%20of%20Topa%20Mastandara%2C%20Mehmood%20Ahmed%2C%20said%20that%20the%20slain%20persons%20were%20among%20eight%20persons%20who%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20Army%20from%20their%20residences%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20deadly%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20and%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20tortured%20to%20death%20by%20the%20Army.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20army%20men%20picked%20up%20several%20civilians%20from%20their%20homes%20on%20Friday%20morning%20besides%20summoning%20a%20few%20of%20them%20to%20their%20camp%20over%20the%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Muhammad%20Siddique%2C%20uncle%20of%20Showkat%2C%20the%20youngest%20among%20the%20three%20dead%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Panch%20of%20the%20locality%2C%20said%20that%20he%20rang%20up%20several%20local%20politicians%20and%20officials%20to%20help%20them%20in%20getting%20them%20released%20from%20custody%20after%20they%20were