p%3ENoor%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20talk.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20shock.%20I%20will%20talk%20to%20you%20after%20the%20funeral%20prayers%20are%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20purported%20video%20clips%20of%20the%20detained%20men%20being%20tortured%20show%20army%20soldiers%20spraying%20chilli%20powder%20on%20their%20buttocks.%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EGand%20Mein%20Dal%20Es%20Ko%20Mirchi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Put%20chilli%20in%20his%20anus)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20soldier%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20also%20shows%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20who%20is%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground%20while%20another%20man%20can%20be%20seen%20moving%20his%20hands%20helplessly%20before%20being%20stripped%20and%20sprayed%20with%20chilli%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20shows%20army%20soldiers%20pushing%20and%20beating%20up%20a%20man%20with%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20plastic%20cane%20while%20he%20is%20pleading%20with%20them%20to%20spare%20him.%20An%20army%20man%20could%20be%20seen%20sitting%20with%20jackboots%20on%20the%20arms%20of%20a%20civilian%20lying%20motionless%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20Poonch%20district%20following%20the%20alleged%20custodial%20deaths.%20Preparations%20are%20underway%20to%20conduct%20their%20last%20rites%20with%20top%20officials%20of%20civil%20and%20police%20administration%20rushing%20to%20the%20area%20while%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20to%20avoid%20any%20law%20and%20order%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20their%20village%20because%20there%20are%20restrictions%20here.%20But%20I%20have%20been%20told%20that%20the%20five%20other%20civilians%20are%20admitted%20in%20the%20army