y%20has%20been%20activated%20to%20trace%20the%20attackers%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20the%20dense%20forests%20in%20Surankote%2C%20which%20falls%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20R%20R%20Swain%2C%20General%20Officer%20Commanding%20(GoC)%2C%20XVI%20Corps%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Sandeep%20Jain%20and%20a%20team%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20attack%20in%20Poonch%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division%20which%20has%20witnessed%20a%20dramatic%20spike%20in%20militancy-related%20incidents%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20downgraded%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20violence%20has%20subsided%20in%20Kashmir%20valley%20after%20years%20of%20shutdowns%2C%20clashes%20and%20encounters%20involving%20civilians%2C%20militants%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20theatre%20of%20insurgency%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20where%2024%20militants%20were%20killed%20this%20year%20while%2021%20army%20soldiers%20also%20laid%20down%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20civilians%20have%20also%20been%20killed%20in%20conflict-related%20violence%20in%20the%20twin%20districts%20this%20year%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20124%20people%2C%20including%2083%20militants%20and%2028%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20security%20situation%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20deceased%20are%20two%20army%20and%20police%20officers%2C%20including%20a%20Colonel%20and%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20week-long%20Kokernag%20encounter%20in%20south%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20three%20labourers%20from%20Rajouri%20district%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20staged%20gun%20battle%20by%20the%20Army%20in%20Amshipora%20village%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20district%20and%20passed%20off%20as%20terrorists%2C%20reportedly%20for%20cash%20reward%20and%20quick%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20an%20Army%20Captain%20identified%20as%20Bhoopendra%20Singh%20alias%20Major%20Basheer%20Khan%20had%20abducted%20the%20three%20young%20men%20in%20a%20private%20car%20from%20their%20rented%20accommodation%20at%20Chowgam%20Shopian%2C%20killed%20them%20and%20later%20planted%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20weapons%20and%20material%20on%20their%20dead%20bodies%20and%20tried%20to%20tag%20them%20as%20hardcore%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703325532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fcivilians-killed-in-the-aftermath-of-poonch-terror-attack-were-tortured-to-death-allege-families%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20alleged%20custodial%20killing%20of%20the%20three%20civilians%20triggered%20protests%20in%20Poonch%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fcivilians-killed-in-the-aftermath-of-poonch-terror-attack-were-tortured-to-death-allege-families%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Kuki%20Tribal%20Body%20to%20Seal%20Borders%20between%20Hill%2C%20Valley%20Districts%20During%20Christmas%20Season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08131052%2FF7SQIIebEAAHp2K.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2