this%20morning%20(December%2022)%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20Israeli%2098th%20Division%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20the%20attack%20in%20South%20Gaza%2C%20has%20said%20the%20war%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20take%20years%20in%20order%20to%20win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Halevy%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20claim%2C%20made%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20war%2C%20that%20Israel%20would%20%E2%80%9Cannihilate%E2%80%9D%20Hamas%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20unfortunate%20statement%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20obtain%20this%20result%E2%80%9D.%20Halevy%20agreed%20that%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20set%20itself%20an%20unachievable%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20best%20way%20of%20dealing%20with%20Hamas%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20talk%20to%20Hamas%20and%20not%20only%20fight%20Hamas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiden-guns-shipment-delay-israel%5C%22%3EThe%20Biden%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20Delay%20of%20Gun%20Shipments%20to%20Israel%20Police%20Is%20Simply%20Too%20Little%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Halevy%20recounts%20in%20some%20detail%20the%20attempt%20to%20murder%20former%20Hamas%20chief%20Khaled%20Mashal%20around%202007-2008%20by%20administering%20poison%20to%20him%20and%20how%20that%20opened%20a%20window%2C%20proposed%20to%20him%20as%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20by%20King%20Hussein%20of%20Jordan%2C%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ehudna%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20Arabic%20for%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20he%20says%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%20failed%20to%20grab%20this%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20awful%20lot%20in%20this%20interview%20with%20Halevy%20which%20I%20am%20not%20revealing%20because%20I%20think%20you%20should%20hear%20it%20for%20yourself.%20Let%20me%20instead%20reiterate%20that%20Halevy%20is%20possibly%20the%20most%20highly%20regarded%20former%20head%20of%20intelligence%20in%20Israel.%20He%20has%20spoken%20with%20incredible%20candour%2C%20detail%20and%20with%20a%20great%20amount%20of%20revelation%20of%20things%20that%20he%20has%20personally%20known%20and%20seen%20in%20his%20illustrious%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20you%2C%20I%20include%20below%20the%20questions.%20They%20will%20give%20you%20some%20sense%20of%20how%20the%20conversation%20develops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20must%20see%20the%20conversation%20for%20yourself.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20any%20other%20head%20of%20Mossad%20and%20any%20other%20head%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Council%20has%20spoken%20so%20fully%20to%20an%20Indian%20audience%2C%20or%20perhaps%20any%20audience%20on%20a%20television%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20last%20ten%20weeks%20since%20October%207%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20become%20clear%20that%20there%20were%20multiple%20intelligence%20and%20military%20failures%20on%20October%207%20when%20Hamas%20attacked%20Israel.%20However%2C%20what%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20is%20how%20serious%20they%20were%20and%20at%20what%20sort%20of%20levels%20they%20occurred.%20Could%20you%20start%20by%20giving%20me%20some%20idea%20of%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Prior%20to%20October%207%2C%20Israel%20went%20through%20a%20period%20of%20some%20nine%20months%20of%20political%20turmoil%20with%20tens%20of%20thousands%20protesting%20on%20the%20streets%20against%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20judicial%20reforms.%20To%20what%20extent%20did%20that%20turmoil%20play%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20advantage%2C%20whilst%20weakening%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E3.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20former%20head%20of%20Mossad%20and%20former%20head%20of%20the%20Isra