20not%20to%20demean%20and%20push%20them%20to%20the%20limits%20of%20retirement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punia%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20further%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrestler-bajrang-punia-says-he-is-returning-his-padma-shri-to-pm-modi-amid-wrestling-body-row-4722726%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20not%20given%20due%20respect%2C%20I%20do%20not%20deserve%20this%20honour%20either.%20We%20were%20on%20the%20road%20for%2040%20days%2C%20but%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20government%20have%20not%20been%20fulfilled.%20Our%20fight%20is%20not%20against%20the%20government%2C%20but%20against%20an%20individual.%20I%20believe%20in%20the%20judiciary%20but%2C%20with%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20give%20up%20wrestling.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20not%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20my%20wrestling%20career%2C%20and%20I%20am%20preparing%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20open%20letter%20to%20Modi%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CSports%20have%20empowered%20our%20women%20athletes%20and%20changed%20their%20lives%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20the%20women%20who%20could%20have%20been%20the%20brand%20ambassadors%20of%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%20are%20now%20leaving%20the%20sport.%20And%20we%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20who%20were%20awarded%2C%20could%20not%20do%20anything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20election%20as%20WFI%20chief%2C%20his%20letter%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20shed%20tears%20the%20entire%20night.%20We%20did%20not%20understand%20what%20to%20do%20or%20where%20to%20go.%20The%20government%20has%20given%20us%20a%20lot.%20I%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202019%20and%20I%20also%20received%20the%20Arjuna%20and%20Khel%20Ratna%20awards.%20When%20I%20got%20these%20awards%2C%20I%20was%20on%20cloud%20nine.%20But%20today%20the%20sadness%20weighs%20more%20and%20the%20reason%20is%20a%20women%20wrestler%20left%20the%20sport%20because%20of%20(fears%20over)%20her%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20official%20provision%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98return%E2%80%99%20of%20Padma%20awards.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20someone%20sought%20to%20%E2%80%98return%E2%80%99%20their%20award%3B%20in%202020%2C%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Prakash%20Singh%20Badal%20%E2%80%98returned%E2%80%99%20his%20Padma%20award%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20enacted%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20an%20awardee%20may%20announce%20his%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20award%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20Padma%20Awards%20regulations%20do%20not%20cover%20this%20eventuality.%20They%20only%20allow%20cancellation%20and%20annulment%20of%20the%20awards%20by%20the%20President%2C%20without%20specifying%20the%20grounds.%20The%20awardee%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20the%20register%20of%20Padma%20recipients%20maintained%20under%20directions%20of%20the%20President%2C%20until%20his%2Fher%20award%20is%20annulled.%20The%20rules%20provide%20for%20cancellation%20of%20such%20annulment%20by%20the%20President%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fone-can-check-out-in-padma-protest-but-can-never-leave%2Farticleshow%2F106222382.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703313900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23120753%2FEffect-42.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcant-live-as-padma-shri-awardee-when-women-wrestlers-are-insulted-bajrang-punia-to-pm-modi%22%2C%22s