2F166057%2Findia-surgery-robot-innovation-gujarat-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobotic%20surgeries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20patients%20went%20home%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20performed%20so%20many%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20would%20come%20to%20India%20to%20train%20people%20in%20robotic%20surgeries.%20Back%20then%2C%20India%20did%20not%20have%20its%20own%20robotic%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202002%2C%20he%20performed%20his%20first%20robotic%20surgery%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20country%20but%20in%202011%2C%20I%20got%20an%20offer%20from%20a%20major%20hospital%20to%20launch%20their%20robotic%20surgery%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20says%20he%20had%20always%20longed%20to%20be%20back%20home%2C%20so%20he%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity%2C%20packed%20his%20bags%2C%20and%20moved%20back%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20there%20were%20only%20six%20to%20seven%20robotic%20systems%2C%20that%20too%20exported%2C%20so%20there%20were%20not%20many%20patients%20that%20could%20afford%20to%20pay%20those%20two%20to%20three%20lakh%20rupees%20more%20for%20robotic%20surgery.%20It%20was%20around%20this%20time%20when%20I%20met%20the%2022-year-old%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20incident%20made%20the%20doctor%20realise%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20a%20system%20that%20is%20cheaper.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20the%20high%20costs%20we%20cannot%20offer%20the%20best%20treatment%20to%20the%20patients%2C%20and%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20we%20have%20to%20develop%20it%20in%20the%20country%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20doctor%20made%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause%20and%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20practice%20on%20hold%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20done%20over%201%2C400%20surgeries%20and%20with%